Topic : Weather Date and Time Wizard

This app provides a visual indication of weather as well as time-zone across different location based on the configuration.By default we can find Bangalore location weather and Asia/Calcutta(Time zone) specific date and time.

Preference Setting

1. Set Location : In help view page, All  locations are mentioned that is a combination of city, country and continent.
so copy the location title from there.
 
2. Time Zone : Here we can select time-zone.

3. Metric : Here we can select temperature either in celsius or fahrenheit.


OS       : Windows 7
Liferay  : 6.1.0+ Version
DataBase : Mysql5.5
Language : PHP 5
